msgid "List subscription plans"
msgstr "Daftar rencana langganan"

msgid ""
"Get all available subscription plans.\n"
"\n"
"        **Filtering**: Only returns active and public plans unless user is "
"staff.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Display available subscription options to customers "
"during checkout or on pricing pages.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Public endpoint - no authentication required."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan semua rencana langganan yang tersedia.\n"
"\n"
"**Penyaringan**: Hanya mengembalikan rencana yang aktif dan umum kecuali "
"pengguna adalah staf.\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Tampilkan opsi langganan yang tersedia kepada "
"pelanggan saat checkout atau pada halaman harga.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Titik akhir umum - tidak diperlukan otentikasi."

msgid "Get subscription plan details"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail rencana langganan"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific subscription plan.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Show plan details before subscription creation or on "
"plan comparison pages.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Public endpoint - no authentication required."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan informasi terperinci tentang rencana langganan tertentu.\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Tampilkan detail rencana sebelum pembuatan langganan "
"atau pada halaman perbandingan rencana.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Titik akhir umum - tidak memerlukan otentikasi."

msgid "List payment tokens"
msgstr "Daftar token pembayaran"

msgid ""
"Get all payment tokens for the authenticated user.\n"
"\n"
"        **Filtering**: Only returns active tokens unless user is staff.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Show saved payment methods to users when subscribing "
"or updating subscription payment method.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only see their own "
"tokens."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan semua token pembayaran untuk pengguna yang telah diotentikasi.\n"
"\n"
"**Penyaringan**: Hanya mengembalikan token yang aktif kecuali pengguna "
"adalah staf.\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Tampilkan metode pembayaran yang disimpan kepada "
"pengguna saat berlangganan atau memperbarui metode pembayaran langganan.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat melihat token "
"mereka sendiri."

msgid "Get payment token details"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail token pembayaran"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific payment token.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only access their "
"own tokens."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan informasi terperinci tentang token pembayaran tertentu.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat mengakses token "
"mereka sendiri."

msgid "Create payment token"
msgstr "Buat token pembayaran"

msgid ""
"Create a new payment token for recurring billing.\n"
"\n"
"        **Provider-Specific Data Required**:\n"
"\n"
"        **Stripe**:\n"
"        - `payment_method_id`: From Stripe.js on frontend\n"
"        - `set_as_default`: Boolean\n"
"\n"
"        **Square**:\n"
"        - `card_nonce`: From Square Payment Form\n"
"        - `billing_postal_code`: Cardholder ZIP\n"
"        - `cardholder_name`: Cardholder name\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Save a payment method for recurring subscription "
"billing.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Rate limited to prevent abuse."
msgstr ""
"Buat token pembayaran baru untuk pembayaran berulang.\n"
"\n"
"**Data yang Diperlukan Berdasarkan Pemroses**:\n"
"\n"
"**Stripe**:\n"
"- `payment_method_id`: Dari Stripe.js di frontend\n"
"- `set_as_default`: Boolean\n"
"\n"
"**Square**:\n"
"- `card_nonce`: Dari Form Pembayaran Square\n"
"- `billing_postal_code`: Kode pos pemegang kartu\n"
"- `cardholder_name`: Nama pemegang kartu\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Simpan metode pembayaran untuk pembayaran berlangganan "
"berulang.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Dibatasi laju untuk mencegah "
"penyalahgunaan."

msgid "Payment token created successfully"
msgstr "Token pembayaran berhasil dibuat"

msgid "Invalid payment method data"
msgstr "Data metode pembayaran tidak valid"

msgid "Authentication required"
msgstr "Autentikasi diperlukan"

msgid "Delete payment token"
msgstr "Hapus token pembayaran"

msgid ""
"Delete a payment token.\n"
"\n"
"        **Warning**: Cannot delete token if it's being used by an active "
"subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only delete their "
"own tokens."
msgstr ""
"Hapus token pembayaran.\n"
"\n"
"**Peringatan**: Tidak dapat menghapus token jika sedang digunakan oleh "
"langganan aktif.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat menghapus token "
"mereka sendiri."

msgid "List customer subscriptions"
msgstr "Daftar langganan pelanggan"

msgid ""
"Get all subscriptions for the authenticated user.\n"
"\n"
"        **Filtering**: Supports filtering by status.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Show user's active and past subscriptions in their "
"account dashboard.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only see their own "
"subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan semua langganan untuk pengguna yang telah terautentikasi.\n"
"\n"
"**Penyaringan**: Mendukung penyaringan berdasarkan status.\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Tampilkan langganan aktif dan sebelumnya dari pengguna "
"di dashboard akun mereka.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Membutuhkan autentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat melihat "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Filter by status (trial, active, past_due, paused, canceled, expired)"
msgstr ""
"Saring berdasarkan status (percobaan, aktif, masa tunggu, dijeda, "
"dibatalkan, habis)"

msgid "Get subscription details"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail langganan"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only access their "
"own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan informasi terperinci tentang langganan tertentu.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Membutuhkan autentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat mengakses "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Create subscription"
msgstr "Buat langganan"

msgid ""
"Create a new subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        **Required Fields**:\n"
"        - `plan_id`: UUID of subscription plan\n"
"        - `payment_token_id`: UUID of saved payment token\n"
"\n"
"        **Optional Fields**:\n"
"        - `product_id`: Link subscription to specific product\n"
"        - `variant_id`: Link subscription to specific product variant\n"
"        - `trial_override_days`: Override plan's default trial period\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Subscribe user to a plan during checkout or from "
"pricing page.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Creates subscription for "
"authenticated user."
msgstr ""
"Buat langganan baru.\n"
"\n"
"**Field yang Diperlukan**:\n"
"- `plan_id`: UUID dari rencana langganan\n"
"- `payment_token_id`: UUID dari token pembayaran yang disimpan\n"
"\n"
"**Field Opsional**:\n"
"- `product_id`: Hubungkan langganan ke produk tertentu\n"
"- `variant_id`: Hubungkan langganan ke variasi produk tertentu\n"
"- `trial_override_days`: Tambahkan hari uji coba untuk menggantikan periode "
"uji coba default rencana\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Langgankan pengguna ke rencana selama checkout atau "
"dari halaman harga.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Membuat langganan untuk pengguna yang "
"telah diotentikasi."

msgid "Subscription created successfully"
msgstr "Langganan berhasil dibuat"

msgid "Invalid subscription data"
msgstr "Data langganan tidak valid"

msgid "Cancel subscription"
msgstr "Batal langganan"

msgid ""
"Cancel a subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        **Options**:\n"
"        - `immediately`: If true, cancel immediately; otherwise cancel at "
"period end\n"
"        - `reason`: Optional cancellation reason for analytics\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Allow users to cancel their subscription from account "
"settings.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only cancel their "
"own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Batalkan langganan.\n"
"\n"
"**Opsi**:\n"
"- `segera`: Jika benar, batalkan segera; jika tidak, batalkan di akhir "
"periode\n"
"- `alasan`: Alasan pembatalan opsional untuk analitik\n"
"\n"
"**Penggunaan**: Izinkan pengguna membatalkan langganan mereka dari "
"pengaturan akun.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat membatalkan "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Subscription canceled successfully"
msgstr "Langganan berhasil dibatalkan"

msgid "Cannot cancel subscription"
msgstr "Tidak dapat membatalkan langganan"

msgid "Subscription not found"
msgstr "Langganan tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Pause subscription"
msgstr "Jeda langganan"

msgid ""
"Pause a subscription temporarily.\n"
"\n"
"        **Options**:\n"
"        - `reason`: Optional pause reason\n"
"        - `auto_resume_date`: Optional date to automatically resume\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Allow users to pause subscription during vacation or "
"temporary inactivity.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only pause their "
"own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Jeda langganan secara sementara.\n"
"\n"
"**Opsi**:\n"
"- `alasan`: Alasan jeda opsional\n"
"- `auto_resume_date`: Tanggal opsional untuk melanjutkan secara otomatis\n"
"\n"
"**Penggunaan**: Izinkan pengguna menjeda langganan selama liburan atau "
"ketidaktahuan sementara.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat menjeda langganan "
"mereka sendiri."

msgid "Subscription paused successfully"
msgstr "Langganan berhasil dijeda"

msgid "Cannot pause subscription"
msgstr "Tidak dapat menjeda langganan"

msgid "Resume subscription"
msgstr "Lanjutkan langganan"

msgid ""
"Resume a paused subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Allow users to resume paused subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only resume their "
"own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Lanjutkan langganan yang dijeda.\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Izinkan pengguna untuk melanjutkan langganan yang "
"dijeda.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Membutuhkan autentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat melanjutkan "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Subscription resumed successfully"
msgstr "Langganan berhasil dilanjutkan"

msgid "Cannot resume subscription"
msgstr "Tidak dapat melanjutkan langganan"

msgid "Update payment method"
msgstr "Perbarui metode pembayaran"

msgid ""
"Update subscription payment method.\n"
"\n"
"        **Required Field**:\n"
"        - `payment_token_id`: UUID of new payment token\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Allow users to change credit card used for "
"subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only update their "
"own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Perbarui metode pembayaran langganan.\n"
"\n"
"**Field Wajib**:\n"
"- `payment_token_id`: UUID dari token pembayaran baru\n"
"\n"
"**Penggunaan**: Memungkinkan pengguna mengganti kartu kredit yang digunakan "
"untuk langganan.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Membutuhkan autentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat memperbarui "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Payment method updated successfully"
msgstr "Metode pembayaran berhasil diperbarui"

msgid "Invalid payment token"
msgstr "Token pembayaran tidak valid"

msgid "Get billing history"
msgstr "Dapatkan riwayat pembayaran"

msgid ""
"Get billing history for a subscription.\n"
"\n"
"        Shows all billing attempts, successful and failed, with retry "
"information.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Display subscription billing history to users.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only view their own "
"subscription history."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan riwayat pembayaran untuk langganan.\n"
"\n"
"Menampilkan semua upaya pembayaran, berhasil dan gagal, dengan informasi "
"pengulangan.\n"
"\n"
"**Penggunaan**: Tampilkan riwayat pembayaran langganan kepada pengguna.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Membutuhkan autentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat melihat riwayat "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Billing history retrieved successfully"
msgstr "Riwayat pembayaran berhasil diambil"

msgid "Change subscription plan"
msgstr "Ubah rencana langganan"

msgid ""
"Change the subscription to a different plan.\n"
"\n"
"        **Required Fields**:\n"
"        - `new_plan_id`: UUID of the new subscription plan\n"
"        - `new_tier_id`: UUID of the new pricing tier\n"
"\n"
"        **Optional Fields**:\n"
"        - `mode`: 'auto' (default, uses plan-configured behavior), "
"'immediate', or 'at_renewal'\n"
"\n"
"        **Behavior**:\n"
"        - **Upgrades**: By default applied immediately with prorated charge\n"
"        - **Downgrades**: By default deferred to next renewal with prorated "
"credit\n"
"        - The `mode` parameter overrides plan-configured behavior\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only change their "
"own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Ubah langganan ke rencana yang berbeda.\n"
"\n"
"**Field Wajib**:\n"
"- `new_plan_id`: UUID dari rencana langganan baru\n"
"- `new_tier_id`: UUID dari tingkat harga baru\n"
"\n"
"**Field Opsional**:\n"
"- `mode`: 'auto' (default, menggunakan perilaku yang dikonfigurasi oleh "
"rencana), 'immediate', atau 'at_renewal'\n"
"\n"
"**Perilaku**:\n"
"- **Peningkatan**: Secara default diterapkan segera dengan biaya prorata\n"
"- **Penurunan**: Secara default ditunda hingga pembaruan berikutnya dengan "
"kredit prorata\n"
"- Parameter `mode` mengatasi perilaku yang dikonfigurasi oleh rencana\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Membutuhkan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat mengubah "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Plan changed or scheduled successfully"
msgstr "Rencana berhasil diubah atau dijadwalkan"

msgid "Cannot change plan"
msgstr "Tidak dapat mengubah rencana"

msgid "Cancel scheduled plan change"
msgstr "Batalkan perubahan rencana yang dijadwalkan"

msgid ""
"Cancel a pending scheduled plan change.\n"
"\n"
"        If a plan change is scheduled for the next billing cycle, this "
"action\n"
"        cancels it and keeps the current plan.\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: User changed their mind about a deferred plan change.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only modify their "
"own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Batalkan perubahan rencana yang telah dijadwalkan.\n"
"\n"
"Jika perubahan rencana dijadwalkan untuk siklus pembayaran berikutnya, "
"tindakan ini\n"
"membatalkannya dan mempertahankan rencana saat ini.\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Pengguna berubah pikiran mengenai perubahan rencana "
"yang ditunda.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Membutuhkan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat memodifikasi "
"langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Scheduled change canceled"
msgstr "Perubahan yang dijadwalkan dibatalkan"

msgid "No scheduled change to cancel"
msgstr "Tidak ada perubahan yang dijadwalkan untuk dibatalkan"

msgid "Reactivate canceled subscription"
msgstr "Aktifkan kembali langganan yang dibatalkan"

msgid ""
"Reactivate a previously canceled subscription within the reactivation "
"window.\n"
"\n"
"        **Optional Fields**:\n"
"        - `payment_token_id`: UUID of payment token (uses existing if not "
"provided)\n"
"\n"
"        **Behavior**:\n"
"        - Starts a new billing period from today\n"
"        - For native providers: creates a new provider subscription\n"
"        - Requires the reactivation deadline to not have passed\n"
"\n"
"        **Use Case**: Allow customers to resubscribe after canceling, using "
"the same plan and settings.\n"
"\n"
"        **Security**: Requires authentication. Users can only reactivate "
"their own subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Reaktifkan langganan yang sebelumnya dibatalkan dalam jendela reaktifasi.\n"
"\n"
"**Bidang Opsional**:\n"
"- `payment_token_id`: UUID token pembayaran (akan menggunakan yang sudah ada "
"jika tidak disediakan)\n"
"\n"
"**Perilaku**:\n"
"- Memulai periode pembayaran baru mulai hari ini\n"
"- Untuk penyedia bawaan: membuat langganan penyedia baru\n"
"- Memerlukan agar batas waktu reaktifasi belum terlewat\n"
"\n"
"**Kasus Penggunaan**: Memungkinkan pelanggan untuk berlangganan kembali "
"setelah membatalkan, menggunakan rencana dan pengaturan yang sama.\n"
"\n"
"**Keamanan**: Memerlukan otentikasi. Pengguna hanya dapat mengaktifkan "
"kembali langganan mereka sendiri."

msgid "Subscription reactivated successfully"
msgstr "Langganan berhasil diaktifkan kembali"

msgid "Cannot reactivate subscription"
msgstr "Tidak dapat mengaktifkan kembali langganan"

msgid "Subscriptions"
msgstr "Langganan"

msgid "Tiered Pricing"
msgstr "Harga Berlapis"

msgid "Quantity-Based"
msgstr "Berdasarkan Jumlah"

msgid "Flat Rate"
msgstr "Tarif Tetap"

msgid "Cancel Anytime"
msgstr "Batal Kapan Saja"

msgid "Cancel at Period End"
msgstr "Batal di Akhir Periode"

msgid "Minimum Commitment Required"
msgstr "Komitmen Minimum Diperlukan"

msgid "Plan ID"
msgstr "ID Rencana"

msgid "Unique identifier for this plan"
msgstr "Identifikasi unik untuk rencana ini"

msgid "Plan Name"
msgstr "Nama Rencana"

msgid "Name displayed to customers (e.g., 'Premium Plan', 'Enterprise Plan')"
msgstr ""
"Nama yang ditampilkan kepada pelanggan (misalnya, 'Rencana Premium', "
"'Rencana Enterprise')"

msgid "Slug"
msgstr "Slug"

msgid "URL-friendly version of the name"
msgstr "Versi nama yang ramah URL"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Deskripsi"

msgid "Detailed description of what this plan includes"
msgstr "Deskripsi rinci tentang apa yang termasuk dalam rencana ini"

msgid "Translations"
msgstr "Terjemahan"

msgid "Multilingual content for customer-facing fields (name, description)"
msgstr ""
"Konten multibahasa untuk bidang yang menghadap ke pelanggan (nama, deskripsi)"

msgid "Pricing Model"
msgstr "Model Harga"

msgid "How pricing is structured for this plan"
msgstr "Bagaimana struktur harga untuk rencana ini"

msgid "Allow Quantity"
